media: pt1: use #ifdef CONFIG_PM_SLEEP instead of #if

As pointed by ktest:

>> drivers/media//pci/pt1/pt1.c:1433:5: warning: "CONFIG_PM_SLEEP" is not defined, evaluates to 0 [-Wundef]
    #if CONFIG_PM_SLEEP
        ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

